Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.77,0:01:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mana will be reborn by consuming Inori.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.19,0:01:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our lost Eve...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.29,0:01:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too late,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.79,0:01:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.54,0:01:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.57,0:02:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.92,0:02:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.31,0:02:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's starting to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. We'll hold them off here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.48,0:02:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go up as quickly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase! Cover them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.78,0:02:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger! But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really got me last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this time will be different!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.12,0:02:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I have the Gespenst!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.34,0:02:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi, you still can't take back control?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The defenses suddenly got stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I keep trying to erase it, but it keeps coming back like a zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone on par with Tsugumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenji...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Triton.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you're awake, Mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.39,0:03:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was this annoying woman who kept getting in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I crushed her and took this body for my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was she thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That manmade monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.91,0:03:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inori's no monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:04:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She cried for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look and sound the same, but she's not like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's human!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're mean, Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your big sister loves you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I loved you even when my body was blown to shreds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you reject me again, Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.54,0:04:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the rest to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hurt me, Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hurt someone, you must be prepared to receive the same amount in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if you apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's started, Gai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's genomic resonance values higher than Lost Christmas coming from Tokyo{24区\an8}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's even affecting the Endlave remote control system!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fourth Apocalypse has started.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The evolution and selection of life on this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Discard our weak bodies and achieve an eternal consciousness within the crystals.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the next stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Voids were just a sign of a new world,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where hearts are material!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you're using normal weaponry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll crush you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate us, you son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase! Connect with a cable!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi! An evasion program!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:07:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Daryl!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Void Genome Emulator is still being tested!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't overuse it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.93,0:08:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't stop until I've butchered them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.26,0:08:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Souta!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.73,0:08:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back in Roppongi, you said you'd save Mana!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You told me to stab you to save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did it come to this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't understand, Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.13,0:08:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were chosen, yet you chose to let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could never understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it, Kurosu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl you tried to save is ending the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did this to the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Shu... just for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not deny it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to shoot me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let them through.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will hold them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How persistent!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I can't keep up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold out until my signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you're talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, I would've let you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have Mana and the place of Adam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now, you're unworthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die, Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body's numb.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I going to die here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With everyone's Void's in me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.74,0:10:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up, Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can still move.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,use me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenji,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's checkmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.56,0:11:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are people
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.23,0:11:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who trusted me with their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:12:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will get Inori back for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase, sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave remote control to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.47,0:12:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll defeat you with all I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it. You're there, aren't you?!{chinchikurin, his "nickname" for tsugumi}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.03,0:12:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I take you out, I can be myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can be Daryl the butcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! We'll fry you first!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inori?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, the winner was neither Kurosu nor I.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.77,0:13:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Haruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just stay yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.18,0:14:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The place where selection converges.{literal. i have no idea.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world beyond the Apocalypse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.23,0:14:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.73,0:14:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the utopia of the Da'at.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This whole planet will turn into
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.28,0:14:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,memories inside the crystals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.24,0:14:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been celebrated as a king,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but in the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have always been afraid of being selected out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the reason why
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.18,0:15:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted Eve...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.26,0:15:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back there,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you stabbed us in Roppongi,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believed that Mana would be freed that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.61,0:15:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Da'at,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the will of the natural selection
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.11,0:15:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will not allow Mana to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she died{lit rot}, she'd just be reanimated again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is just one way to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is to let her finish her role.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I risked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would become the devil myself and bring about the Apocalypse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you would come to stop us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My role ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.02,0:16:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now go
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and save Inori.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.47,0:16:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.35,0:16:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,got a lot of feelings from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.11,0:16:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:16:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.39,0:17:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inori...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:17:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:18:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Ouma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.43,0:18:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu! Are you going to become the new Savior!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The entire framework is in havoc because of the Genome Crystal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.53,0:18:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole building will collapse soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.16,0:18:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Ouma! Are you unhurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.29,0:18:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get another chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.76,0:18:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,be more kind to people!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.05,0:18:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deep down, you were a nice guy, Daryl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel the hearts of everyone flowing towards me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.61,0:18:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:19:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the people who hated me were born
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and loved by someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inori...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.42,0:19:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inori!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Shu's still in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I can't let you die here either!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.88,0:20:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.61,0:21:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yahiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're early.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're busy with work?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinda.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I left early today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.79,0:21:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I sit here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.04,0:21:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.50,0:21:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase, you're okay with an Earl Gray?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.88,0:21:25.88,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}These days you love me no more
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.88,0:21:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so nice of you, Tsugumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.72,0:21:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher exams are coming up, so I'll turn into a demon again at home.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.51,0:21:32.52,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}nor am I still treasured by you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be here.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.89,0:21:41.32,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}Now I am all alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.31,0:21:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.10,0:21:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, there he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.56,0:21:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.11,0:21:49.20,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}What did you tell me when we parted?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.82,0:21:55.83,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}The words hung in midair and never reached me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.16,0:21:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, to this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.16,0:21:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.29,0:22:02.59,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}I know my dreams and wishes are illusory
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.17,0:22:09.22,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}and yet I cannot give up on them
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.31,0:22:19.27,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}You said, "Don't let go, hold onto my hand"
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.81,0:22:26.28,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}and, "We will always be together"
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.44,0:22:35.04,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}Your hands as I held them were warm
Dialogue: 1,0:22:38.16,0:22:43.34,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,2000)}and tender
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:22:54.82,signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\an7\c&H000000&\pos(1110,142)}Thank you \Nvery much \Nfor watching \Nuntil now!
